adstage:network_company.name: Foxtail Marketing
adstage:network_company.description:
Foxtail Marketing is a digital marketing firm that provides content marketing, digital marketing, and lead generation services for mid-market companies.  The content we create focuses on engagement and lead generation.  Our sole goal for our clients is to enhance their brand, drive traffic, and increase revenues.

We handle everything from content creation to the distribution of the content and then the nurturing of the leads generated by the content.  Our tactics create reliable and replicable lead generation and conversion tactics for business-to-business focused companies.

Our work is shared more socially, valued more by Google, and produces better results than anything else in the industry.

“The best people and best products, producing the best results for our clients.”

title.placeholder: Give your goal a short title
title.hint: Create a title clearly associated with your chosen goal. This will let you quickly distinguish it from your other campaign goals.
title.title: Goal Title

url.title: Goal Url (without domain)
url.hint:
Where do users have to go for your goal to be reached?
          Maybe it's your product page or maybe it's just your homepage.
          Both can give you an indication of customer engagement.
          (ie. For AdStage, our goal is for people to reach the
          post sign up page indicating they want to check out the site.)

match_type.title: Match Type
match_type.hint:
Exact: This is an exact match on every exact character in your URL. If your URLs are easy to read, use this type of match
          <br/>
          Head: This matches characters of a URL up to the end of a string you specify, but excludes the parameters after what you explicitly include. If you have lots of similar URLs, with slight changes at the end of the URL, this is the best matching type to use.
          <br/>
          Regular expression: This is the most flexible matching type, in cases where you include special characters or your URL changes significantly.

goal_value.title: Goal value (optional)
goal_value.hint: Set goal values for your campaigns if you value one goal conversion more highly than others, you can value your different goals in order of importance.
